storyInfo: Having left the boxing ring, Beehunter encounters her one-time nemesis and gets a chance to close out that unfinished bout.

attributes.content: 2:19 P.M. \ Clear
Village on the Ursus outskirts
*Gulp* Ah! This is some good beer. Fresh and smooth.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Ahem... Miss Shura...
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: Why the long face, boss? The beer here's made with local honey. It's great!
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Plus, you're leaving tomorrow, and this is my last day working for you. Have one on me!
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Absolutely not. I like to keep a balanced diet. I'm not in the habit of finishing a whole can of honey in the middle of the night, then binging sweetened booze the next day.
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: You were the one who said I could help myself to what's in the fridge!
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Yeah, but, you know, within reason...
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: Don't you worry about your health?
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: Being a bodyguard is hard work. Need the fat and the sugar to get enough energy.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Like I said, 'within reason'!
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: Haha, gotcha, boss.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Sigh...
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: Say, I wanted to ask, do you have any plans after this job is over?
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: (Scratches head) I've thought about it, but I haven't come up with an answer.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Actually, I wanted to talk to you—
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: Promotion on freshly-brewed honey beer! Buy one, get one free!
attributes.name: Waiter

attributes.content: I'll have another!
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: One special honey beer, coming right up!
attributes.name: Waiter

attributes.content: —about this.
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: Did you say something? Couldn't hear.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: *sigh*...
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: I can't stay any longer, Shura, but there's something important that I want to tell you. This is no place to talk.
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: Of course, boss. With you all the way.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: You... huh? What's that...?
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: Why aren't you moving? Aren't you in a hurry?
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Am I seeing things, Shura? Looks like there's someone running towards us.
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: He's heading straight for you! Darn it, I knew the agent was lying when he said your background was clean!
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: Wait a minute! I told you, all I did was underground boxing. I've never been in the mob!
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Really? That man looks like he's pretty eager to talk to you.
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: Er... well, actually, I do know him. Relax, just get behind me.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Well, if it isn't our boxing champion.
attributes.name: Muscular Man

attributes.content: Get out of the way, Yevgeny. I don't have time for you right now.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: You quit boxing to become a bodyguard? Oh, I forgot, you're not a champion anymore.
attributes.name: Muscular Man

attributes.content: Only an ass like you would celebrate a champion belt won for free.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Shura...
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: (It's like she's a completely different person.)
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: It wouldn't have been hard to take the belt from a rookie like you.
attributes.name: Muscular Man

attributes.content: Oh yeah? Maybe you won't talk so loud with your nose snapped in half.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: You think you would be running your mouth like this if I didn't get ambushed the day before the match?
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Say, you...
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: Stop making excuses. It won't change the fact that you never showed up to the match.
attributes.name: Muscular Man

attributes.content: You have no shame, do you, asshole?
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Oh, mad now? What would the old man think, I wonder, if he knew that his finest student was licking boots as a bodyguard?
attributes.name: Muscular Man

attributes.content: Don't you dare mention my coach!
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Ooh, getting all puffed up in the cheeks, eh? Should we take this outside?
attributes.name: Muscular Man

attributes.content: That's enough!
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: Shura, I don't care what grudge you have against him, but your time doesn't belong to you. It belongs to the one paying your fee, in other words, me!
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: So please don't waste your time and my money on... er... THAT.
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: Huh? Um, yeah, listen to boss girl and run away with your tail between your legs!
attributes.name: Muscular Man

attributes.content: Huh? Isn't our work done already, boss?
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: The work's done, but you're still on duty. I paid you for eight full hours. Let's go, Shura.
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: Alright... can't argue with the contract.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Plus, look at the waiters. They clearly don't want you fighting here.
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: Eh, well, yeah.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: If you aren't gonna fight, Olav, I'm outta here. I'm a busy guy, unlike you.
attributes.name: Muscular Man

attributes.content: If you had the slightest backbone, you wouldn't be showing off your cheap belt.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Let's finish that fight and let the outcome do the talking.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: But not now. I'll come for you later. I know where to find you.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: I bet you're just gonna disappear like last time.
attributes.name: Muscular Man

attributes.content: Oh? Getting cold feet, Mr. Champion?
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: O-Of course not! Bring it on, if you dare... I, I'm not scared of you!
attributes.name: Muscular Man

attributes.content: ARE YOU DONE TALKING YET?
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: Why you suk—!
attributes.name: Muscular Man

attributes.content: Let's go, Shura. We're too busy for... THAT.
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: Gotta go, Yevgeny. See you tonight. You'd better be there.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: 'That'? What does she mean by 'that'?
attributes.name: Muscular Man

attributes.content: 6:34 PM \ Cloudy
So why did you drag me back like this?
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Remember what I told you about Rhodes Island?
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: It's a medicine company, right? The place you work at? You brought it up a bunch of times.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Are you going to keep working as a bodyguard after this job?
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: Who knows? I guess. It's not like people like me have much of a choice.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Well, Rhodes Island is hiring, and I bet you have the skills for the job. I'm thinking of putting in a good word for you with HR.
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: Really? Gosh... thanks, boss.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Plus, it'll only get harder and harder to hide your condition. Even though the authorities are lax out here, things will only get worse if you stay.
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: Sheesh, didn't know you cared about me that much... but is it really okay? You know most places don't tend to hire folks like me, you know, the Infected.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Don't say that. In fact, you're exactly the kind of person we're looking for. Rhodes Island has been striving to make the world better for people like you... people like us.
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: Oh my, I, I don't know how to thank you... I never imagined...
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Don't go to that fight, Shura. You can have a new life. Leave the old one behind.
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: Boss...
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: I don't know how to explain it, but I have to go. It's important to me. I can't leave this place and feel at peace if I don't close the book on it.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: I can't think about tomorrow when there's unfinished business today.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Then tell me about it, Shura. Convince me.
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: I always wanted to put on that championship belt... I'll never have the belt now, but I still want to prove to Coach that I'm worthy of it.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Oh, I see... sorry. I know that he...
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: (Scratches head) Yeah, he's gone.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: When I was little, it was Coach who took me in, taught me how to punch and how to not get punched.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: It was hard enough for him by himself in Ursus, never mind having a kid around... he might have lived a better life if he didn't bother, but that was never on his mind.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: He wanted me to win the belt back all the way to the very end... this is the only thing I can do for him.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: ...I respect your decision, Shura.
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: Thanks, boss.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: I looked into that man's background, and apparently there are some rumors of underhanded happenings... it could be nothing, but be careful nonetheless.
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: Yeah, I'll be careful.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: I'll buy you honey beer, if you win.
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: It's a deal!
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: 10:24 P.M. \ Clear
That suka just won't give up, will she?
attributes.name: Muscular Man

attributes.content: She's a lucky one... can't believe she's still walking after that.
attributes.name: Muscular Man

attributes.content: I should have a talk with the Patrol Unit... make a few rubles while I'm at it.
attributes.name: Muscular Man

attributes.content: Taking to yourself, Yevgeny?
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: O-Olav? How did you know I was here?
attributes.name: Muscular Man

attributes.content: I knew you wouldn't show up to the place, so I tried my luck and waited here.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: I... I was waiting so long that I had to go for a walk!
attributes.name: Muscular Man

attributes.content: Excuses, Yevgeny. If you're scared, you might as well just admit defeat and go home.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: S-Scared? Ha, very funny, Olav...
attributes.name: Muscular Man

attributes.content: Maybe I won't bloody that pretty face of yours if you—
attributes.name: Muscular Man

attributes.content: The man never gets the rest of the sentence out, as he finds himself staring at a fist mere inches from his nose.
Enough talk, idiot. Put your hands up.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: You...
attributes.name: Muscular Man

attributes.content: Try not to bite your tongue, if you really have to talk.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: I-I'll kill you, suka!
attributes.name: Muscular Man

attributes.content: Bring it on!
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: (He's got some weight to his fists. Looks like he's not all talk.)
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Come on, stop dodging and fight me!
attributes.name: Muscular Man

attributes.content: Your fault for being slow! Gotta work harder if you wanna hit me!
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: I'll have your head!
attributes.name: Muscular Man

attributes.content: (His elbows are raised. Now!)
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Take this!
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Her fists finds the man's ribs. Her foe raises his chin in pain, creating an opening.
Shura seizes the opportunity and closes the distance, landing a heavy blow on his chin.
Now!
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: *Cough* *cough* My tooth!
attributes.name: Muscular Man

attributes.content: Ha, big one too.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Wh-Why won't you just die?!
attributes.name: Muscular Man

attributes.content: Die, die, I'm the real champion—
attributes.name: Muscular Man

attributes.content: Yevgeny, you dumbass—
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Wha—who's that? What's that?
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Blame... not the time... offended... you won't...
attributes.name: Shadow

attributes.content: (Can't hear what he's saying, or see his face.)
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Hehe, farewell.
attributes.name: Shadow

attributes.content: Stop—damn it, just before the match...
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: (Is that a gold coin?)
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: The weapon is kicked away and clatters across the ground. Stunned, the man is unable to react.
The Ursus girl grabs his arm and wrestles him to the ground, choking him in a headlock.
What's with the gold coin tattoo?!
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: You... *cough*... help... can't... breathe...
attributes.name: Muscular Man

attributes.content: Speak!
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Argh...
attributes.name: Muscular Man

attributes.content: I've been looking for it for years. It was you all along!
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: It was you who infected me with Oripathy!
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: This is all your fault!
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: I should have been the winner, the one to have my hand held high, the one to win that prize money!
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Help... *choke*...
attributes.name: Muscular Man

attributes.content: It's all your fault, your fault...
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: I should have won that prize money... it would have paid for the old man's medical bills...
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Why did you do that?
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: It wasn't me... the big boss... you wouldn't throw the fight... pissed him off... argh...
attributes.name: Muscular Man

attributes.content: What are you trying to say? You didn't have a choice? You were forced? Let me tell you. You're a coward. This is who you are, and you'll never change, right?
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: I... sorry... was wrong... please... don't...
attributes.name: Muscular Man

attributes.content: Don't kill... me...
attributes.name: Muscular Man

attributes.content: No... enough... shut up...
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Shut up!!!
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.text: It is a common refrain for those on the edge of death.
A plea that goes unheard in the chaotic noise and smell of blood in the underground rings.

attributes.content: ...I can't kill you. I just can't. Dammit.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: I said this was a match... I won't go back on my word.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: I don't kill in the ring. That's a rule I'll never break.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Ugh...
attributes.name: Muscular Man

attributes.content: Look at you, dripping saliva and snot.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: To think that a piece of shit like you ruined my life.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: No, it's not worth it. Not for you.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Argh...
attributes.name: Muscular Man

attributes.content: You're lucky, trash. Get out of my sight.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Ugh... *cough* *pant* *cough*
attributes.name: Muscular Man

attributes.content: My fists are too good to waste on revenge.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Too good for you.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: *Cough*... I'm sorry... I won't do it again... don't kill me... *cough*
attributes.name: Muscular Man

attributes.content: Keep that tongue of yours to yourself. I'll pick up where I left off if I ever hear about you blabbing to the Patrol Unit.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: I, I won't... don't...
attributes.name: Muscular Man

attributes.content: Get out of my sight. I never want to see you again.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Alright, boss, you can come out now. I heard your footsteps ages ago.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: So you weren't sleeping when I left?
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: How could I sleep without the sound of you punching sandbags downstairs?
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: Oops, sorry. I didn't think you could hear me up there.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Honestly. Well, never mind.
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: I thought you were going to kill him.
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: And you didn't think to step in? Man, you're cold-blooded. That scares me.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Give me a break. I'm not that kind of person... and neither are you.
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: You'll really trust me so much, eh?
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: I know you have your principles, Shura.
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: Yeah... I still think of myself as a boxer, even if I don't box anymore.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: The match ends when my opponent is knocked out. A boxer doesn't go any further.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Even if it's not someone worthy to call an opponent?
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: I've boxed for years, boss. Opponents come and go, in all shapes and sizes, but the ring beneath my feet...
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Uh-huh?
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: ...It's always there.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: The ring matters to me. Every punch I throw, I have to be proud.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Well, you weren't exactly boxing in a proper ring just now.
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: But the ring's always in my heart.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: You fought in underground rings, weren't you? It's not easy to stick to principles in a place like that.
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: Yeah. Too many things down there not fit for the light of day. Throwing matches, betting... that's rookie stuff.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: You get to see all the blood and gore you could ever want, if you have a deep enough pocket. Boxers there are less than animals... we're toys at best.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Maybe I would have become like them, a monster that only knows how to kill.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Hey, what's with that relieved look on your face, boss?
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: I just wanted to tell you how happy I am to have you as a colleague.
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: Boss... *sob*
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Man, you're making me blush, boss.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Don't get too carried away. You still have to put together a CV, be interviewed, assessed...
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: Oh, I don't want to think about any of that. Say no more. I just want a big mug of honey beer, then a good night's sleep.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: Sleep, eh? Look at your shoes first.
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: My shoes? Oh, the bottoms are starting to come off. Heh, sorry, I've had these for a long time.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: I think I have an extra pair. Try them on when we get back; see if they fit.
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: Let's head out as soon as possible. Who knows if that guy might change his mind and start running his mouth.
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: Sorry, guess I shouldn't have let him go.
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: No need to apologize. His blood wasn't worth staining...
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator

attributes.content: My super-duper fists?
attributes.name: Shura

attributes.content: No, your path to a new life.
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Field Operator
